FFXIV Venues Directory Dalamud Plugin

FFXIV Venues Directory is an in-game venue directory for Final Fantasy XIV.
It loads approved venue data from api.ffxivvenues.com and shows it in a searchable window with filters and a detail panel.

Features
- Live venue list with refresh support
- Search by name, description, and tags
- Filters by region, data center, world, venue tags, favorites, visited venues, NSFW/SFW, house size, and opening status
- Detailed venue panel with banner, opening schedule, links, copyable address, and per-venue favorite/visited actions

Commands
- /ffxivvenues
  Open the venue directory window.
- /ffxivvenues settings
  Open plugin settings.

How it works
- The plugin requests approved venues from the FFXIV Venues API.
- Venue data is cached in-memory for the current client session and can be refreshed from the UI.
- Banners are loaded on demand and reused across the session to reduce repeated downloads.
